tats don’t seem to increase. You don’t feel anymore powerful than before.Loot is almost non-existent as you mostly find the odd canteen or ammo mag or coins. When you do find a weapon again the stats are all over the place and you don’t really know if it is an improvement or that your marines can even use it.The UI is near unusable as you never really know who you gave the ammo to or understand what the stats are of how they interact. Everything is needlessly pixelated and small making it a chore to read. It’s all ugly to boot.It is just too random, badly designed, ugly, unbalanced and entirely unfair. This is a game that has seriously gone wrong at every level. Utterly unenjoyable and would have refunded it if I had the chance back then and demanded money for the waste of time."
